{-3/2}$ decay\nin time. We also study dependence of the decay time on the density of bosons in\nthe low-density regime and use this to estimate decay time for oscillations in\nthe original spin model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 13 Oct 2016 22:48:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 24 Feb 2017 23:46:44 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-02-28"}
