fits our data satisfactorily, and recovers Zahn's\n1992 model in the limit of large Reynolds numbers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 14 Oct 2016 04:11:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-22"}
